content:
I have completed the full 15-screen iOS app prototype for Taskora. Every screen has been built as a standalone, self-contained HTML file in the `screens/` directory, adhering strictly to the Royal Violet design system and the premium, interactive requirements of the master document.

### Prototype Highlights:
- **Comprehensive Coverage**: All 15 screens from the Splash Screen to the About Screen are fully implemented.
- **Premium Interactions**: Includes animated logo pulses, sideways-expanding workspace panels, interactive calculators, and live status rings.
- **System-Ready Design**: Utilizes SF Pro typography, glassmorphism, and the Royal Violet (#7C3AED) / Fresh Lime (#A3E635) palette.
- **Gallery Launcher**: The root `index.html` provides a master gallery view, showcasing all screens within pixel-accurate iPhone 15 Pro frames.

<artifact identifier="taskora-ios-prototype" type="text/html" title="Taskora iOS Prototype Master Gallery">
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Taskora Prototype - Gallery</title>
  <style>
    :root {
      --bg: #F5F5F4;
      --fg: #111827;
      --muted: #6B7280;
      --accent: #7C3AED;
    }
    body {
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 60px 20px;
      background: #E5E7EB;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 60px;
    }
    .gallery-header {
      text-align: center;
      max-width: 600px;
    }
    .gallery-header h1 {
      font-size: 48px;
      font-weight: 800;
      color: var(--fg);
      margin: 0;
      letter-spacing: -0.04em;
    }
    .gallery-header p {
      font-size: 18px;
      color: var(--muted);
      margin-top: 10px;
    }
    .frames-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(390px, 1fr));
      gap: 60px;
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 1400px;
      justify-items: center;
    }
    .frame-container {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 20px;
    }
    .frame-label {
      font-size: 14px;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: var(--muted);
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.1em;
      background: white;
      padding: 6px 16px;
      border-radius: 20px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
    }
    iframe {
      width: 390px;
      height: 844px;
      border: none;
      border-radius: 54px;
      box-shadow: 0 50px 100px -20px rgba(0,0,0,0.25);
      background: white;
      transition: transform 0.3s;
    }
    iframe:hover {
      transform: translateY(-10px);
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="gallery-header">
    <h1>TASKORA</h1>
    <p>Smart Productivity Workspace — iOS 17 Prototype</p>
  </div>

  <div class="frames-grid">
    <div class="frame-container">
      <span class="frame-label">01 Splash Screen</span>
      <iframe src="/frames/iphone-15-pro.html?screen=screens/01-splash.html" loading="lazy"></iframe>
    </div>
    <div class="frame-container">
      <span class="frame-label">02 Home Dashboard</span>
